<module>
    <h>bodach</h>
    <p><g>bodach</g>
        <en>old man</en> is a masculine <a href="?xx=nouns/simple_common_nouns">simple common
            noun</a>.</p>
    
    <section id="forms">
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>The principal parts of <g>bodach</g> are – <ul>
            <li><m>bodach</m> – nominative/dative singular, genitive plural</li>
            <li><m>bodaich</m> – genitive singular, nominative/dative plural</li>
        </ul>
        </p>
        <section id="definiteness">
            <h>definiteness</h>
            <p><ul>
                <li>indefinite <ul>
                    <li>singular <ul>
                        <li>nominative – <m>bodach</m></li>
                        <li>dative – le <m>bodach</m></li>
                        <li>genitive – ceann <m>bodaich</m></li>
                    </ul></li>
                    <li>plural <ul>
                        <li>nominative – <m>bodaich</m></li>
                        <li>dative – le <m>bodaich</m></li>
                        <li>genitive – cinn <m>bhodach</m></li>
                    </ul></li>
                </ul></li>
                <li>definite <ul>
                    <li>singular <ul>
                        <li>nominative – <m>am bodach</m></li>
                        <li>dative – leis <m>a’ bhodach</m></li>
                        <li>genitive – ceann <m>a’ bhodaich</m></li>
                    </ul></li>
                    <li>plural <ul>
                        <li>nominative – <m>na bodaich</m></li>
                        <li>dative – leis <m>na bodaich</m></li>
                        <li>genitive – cinn <m>nam bodach</m></li>
                    </ul></li>
                </ul></li>
            </ul></p>
        </section>
